{
  "stem": "5626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he explained to us that all the drums we saw when we came into the lager, the camp, were full of gasoline.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were supposed to blow up and burn, completely down, the camp before they will leave the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was the order for the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But our chief in the lager, the German army men, had different idea.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He went on a little German-- they called it the Tiger, which are going through water and dry land, wherever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's a very small, open-top tank.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He went ahead of the American Army with a big white flag, or a sheet, or whatever he had.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then he ask clemency from the army, the American Army men who met him on the road, that he will not go through with the burning down, or the blowing up the camp if himself and his family get the freedom and they can go wherever they want.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Naturally, the-- the army, the American Army, gave him this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They promised him that you will go free.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Just go back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Round up your soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And just give yourself up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You will go free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You will not get harmed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he told us this story also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wished us good luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he even, was funny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, now I had the chance to use my mother's language.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I spoke to you and now I have other duties to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am leaving you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are free to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he warned us, don't go close to the railroad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because it's full of food and that's-- the-- the wagons are-- are full of weapons, German weapons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Naturally, you cannot tell this to a hungry man.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
